**Core Concepts:** SSO allows single authentication for multiple systems. Key terms: Authentication (verify identity), Authorization (grant access), Assertion (signed IdP statement to RP), IdP (authenticates users), RP/SP (relies on assertions), CSP (identity proofing), Federation (cross-domain identity sharing), Trust Agreement (federation terms).
